Written on 166 membrane leaves of average quality, preceded by two 19th-century paper flyleaves and one medieval membrane flyleaf, and followed by one paper flyleaf. 

Fore- and endleaves: fols.ir-iiv blank; fol. iiir, number;
                              fol. iiiv title, bookplate, etc.; fol. Irv, blank.
